item.description: The Audi RS 3 LMS is being developed by Audi Sport customer racing for the relatively new TCR category. This factory-built entry-level race car with its massively flared fenders and low front splitter is reminiscent of a DTM race car, albeit much closer to the production model. The four-cylinder TFSI engine unit delivers up to 350 HP and lets the car accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in about 4.5 seconds and achieves a top speed of up to 265 km/h.

included_in_packs.name: FIA WTCR 2019
included_in_packs.description: The FIA World Touring Car Cup presented by Oscaro, or in short, FIA WTCR, offers the highest standard of tin-top touring car racing on the planet. You can choose between seven cars, including the most recent addition to the grid, the Lynk & Co 03 TCR, all closely matched due to tight regulations and Balance of Performance. These cars are front-wheel-driven, but do not underestimate them: Close racing, hard battles and lots of paint exchange is guaranteed.

included_in_packs.name: Premium Pack
included_in_packs.description: The Premium Pack contains ALL of the content currently available, and will unlock more than 100 cars and 25+ tracks for endless hours of driving pleasure. With one single purchase you will get everything the game has to offer at this particular moment.
